  <description>
    <p>
      This is not a stand alone app. This app is a Python editor for <em>LibreOffice</em> using the <em>LibrePythonista extension</em>.
    </p>
    <p>
      This app add the necessary files and configuration to allow the <em>LibrePythonista extension</em>
      to take advantage of the <em>LibrePythonista python editor</em> in <em>LibreOffice</em> running as a Flatpak.
    </p>
  </description>
